messages.text: Jess, are you there?
Yes. The Monkey is just about to take down the security system so I can get inside the building
Wait five minutes, til the girls are all in their rooms at 2am
Is Eve in place?
Yeah, I left her with my friend Teddy at the bus down the road like we said.
Ah, yes. She just texted me he’s looking at her weird
He’s harmless. Probably just stoned.
And you have him driving the getaway bus!!?
How do you think he drives it the rest of the time??
For fuck’s sake. I knew this was a mistake
I’m sorry I couldn’t track down James Bond and his stretch Escalade. And we don’t have time to argue.
Are you by the back door?
Yes.
There might be a guard there
I already took care of him
What does that mean?
I can handle myself is what it means. He’s a bit knocked out.
What if he wakes up??
He won’t for a while. I knocked him out with a horse tranquilizer
Where did you get a horse tranquilizer??? Nevermind, I don’t want to know.
So now what?
The second you get inside, hang right and duck into the first door to the stairs
The girls are on the 3rd floor. I mentioned that woman you spoke with to that guy Dr. Otto
Is he going to help??
Yes, and he volunteered to get the girls down to you, while I create a diversion
A diversion? That’s vague. What kind of diversion?
There is one clone whose being experimented on, who is already braindead. I’m going to use her
It’s not Emily is it???
No
You better be sure!
I am. Her name is Victoria
Victoria Robbins?
How did you know?
I tried to contact her family from the document I had
Are you inside?
Yes. The Monkey shut down the main system.
I’m on my way up the stairs right now
WAIT. DON’T MOVE
What!? WHY??
Hello??
ANNA??
ANNA??
WTF! If I don’t hear from you in five minutes, I’m coming up there anyway
HOLY SHIT WHAT WAS THAT EXPLODING SOUND!?
That was my diversion! Had to do it early!  Someone was onto me. The girls are coming down the stairs to you!!
YOUR DIVERSION WAS BLOWING SHIT UP!? ARE YOU MAD?? THAT’S GOING TO DRAW SECURITY!
There will be a short time people won’t be sure what is happening. This is the window for you.
DO YOU SEE THE GIRLS AND OTTO??
YES!
Just run with them as fast as you can
What about you??
I’ll be behind you shortly
THIS IS THE SLOPPIEST FUCKING OPERATION
NOT THE TIME FOR JUDGMENT!
I texted Eve to get the bus there now. Text me when you’re on it
Are you there yet??
I’m running them towards the woods first
Just go toward the bus. Do you see it??
YES!
Great, I have one more here! She was in a room by herself!
We’re on our way down! If you have to get on the bus without us, I’ll find a way out with her
WAIT. DON’T GO TO THE BUS
What the hell do you mean don’t go to the bus!?
EVE JUST TEXTED ME THAT SOMETHING WAS WRONG
Like what?!
I just texted her too. She’s not returning my texts
She’s not answering mine either.
I’m walking the girls further into the woods away from here
Where??
Jess?
JESS??
Fuck, I’m coming down there. WHERE ARE YOU???
Take the girl and run in some other direction
What do you mean?
They’re gone and security will find you over here.
What do you mean they’re gone….
Otto pulled a gun on me, had all the girls get on the bus, then tossed Eve and Teddy out of it
They destroyed Eve’s phone
Who’s they!?
I just got this text:
SHIT!
THEY TOOK ADRIENNE?
They got Emily too.
FUCK FUCK FUCK
Where are you right now? Should we wait?
No get out of there
The clone and I are in between cars right now at the side entrance. A security van just pulled up around the back.
Well, the positive side of this is we’ll know where the bus is going
What do you mean?
Since Teddy is such a stoner, he leaves a tracker on it...
so when he drives to concerts he can always find it after the show is over, in case he forgets.
He just has to find where he put his tracker back at his place.
How are you going to get there?
Teddy hotwired one of the cars out here in the lot while we’ve been texting.
Nice friends you have
We’re convenient criminals together, what can I say? We can try to loop around and get you.
Don’t chance it. You’re closer to the exit. We’ll find a way out and text you.
The most important thing is the tracker
The alarms are going crazy. Looks like they overrode The Monkey. Also RUN!!
I’ll be in touch soon. If you don’t hear from me…go get our friends.
Click below to see what happens next...
